{"tid":604922,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[植物撚求救] 點解種棵嘢都咁難","createTime":"2018-03-25T07:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T17:46:24.000Z","uid":159890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f15d0430a82a202ea3f0e26dacc053625b4d01","tid":604922,"uid":159890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"種咗五六年嘢，大多宿命都係俾蟲食哂。喺屋企唔想用藥，試過苦楝，辣椒水效果都唔長久。辣椒水根本整估自己多過整估啲蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係咪因為我屋企植物唔夠，得十幾棵，所以淨係吸引到啲害蟲，吸引唔到啲嘅天敵? 我見街邊啲綠化根本唔會有啲咁嘅問題，係因為夠成立到一個健全嘅 ecosystem。<br />\n<br />\n呢棵辣椒大部分時間都有蚜蟲蹤影，不過從來都未見過咁誇張。而且平時自然啲黑蜘蛛食吓蟲，近排屋企裝修可能趕走咗啲蜘蛛。<br />\n<br />\n就算終有一日真係種得出辣椒，諗起呢個畫面都根本唔會想摘嚟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得好氣餒，啲蟲整極都會不停走返出嚟，我覺得已經去到有心無力嘅地步，係咪放棄會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人有類似嘅問題可以分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/154510_252e43d66acd73dcff5ea7ab9be55058.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F154510_252e43d66acd73dcff5ea7ab9be55058.jpg&h=e83ead21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/154533_711aea13f8694bdd9da856d94f155445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F154533_711aea13f8694bdd9da856d94f155445.jpg&h=c4493cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/154554_a20e6f80d20cdbfac8c4bff50b66b24a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F154554_a20e6f80d20cdbfac8c4bff50b66b24a.jpg&h=f641543a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c3f2eafb0aac98b87b25f56e8e8fd7b03e74a11","tid":604922,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"一買返黎有冇換泥  買外國冇蟲卵嘅泥"},{"pid":"a8d4eb2c94035b8e431976acd36f8c39eaacfc12","tid":604922,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"其實種野真係唔易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf02d047ac37bb7a1acad4b64530483200f14874","tid":604922,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"有冇曬太陽 放係d通風乾爽的地方<br />\n西斜好有用 不過只怕殺埋棵野"},{"pid":"fc7f490563049903ed10f8f72ddcdd2a8d6047ab","tid":604922,"uid":81380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"我都試過水種薄荷, 2 隻唔同品種<br />\n其中一隻一吱營養液俾佢, 第二日訓醒就有蚜蟲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315397af303e4536f2bbdbcb5cc4afceb2a869f1","tid":604922,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:46:24.000Z","msg":"又或者可以睇下有關瓢蟲的資料<br />\n路邊的綠化植物日日都曬到仆街<br />\n而且經常有人修剪同落藥<br />\n你想有蟲都難"}]}